## timed variable

Calls function `fn` without args, prints elapsed time and returns fn's result. The optional `prefix` will be displayed with the output, allowing to label different measurements.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
timed: <T>(fn: () => T, prefix?: string) => T
```
